rows.label: tlk400904_msg0001
rows.name:
I'm not making small talk
with non-customers.

rows.label: tlk400904_msg0002
rows.name:
If you buy something,
I'll be happy to talk.

rows.label: tlk400904_msg0005
rows.name:
I'm definitely not telling
you anything now!

rows.label: tlk400904_msg0006
rows.name:
Thanks for your business!
Now I remember!

rows.label: tlk400904_msg0007
rows.name: It was an old guy named Timell.

rows.label: tlk400904_msg0008
rows.name:
He transports Black Ash and
other ores mined in Superbia.

rows.label: tlk400904_msg0009
rows.name:
He should be working near the
Geothermal Turbine Tower,
just across Midorl Bridge.

rows.label: tlk400904_msg0010
rows.name: Be careful if you go to meet him.
